Quick-start build instructions
------------------------------

1) Generate required scripts:

	sh autogen.sh

2) Configure the package:

	./configure

3) Compile it:

	make

4) Install it:

	make install

More detailed build instructions
--------------------------------

   Requirements

   To build Zephir Library you'll need Autoconf, Automake, and friends
   (collectively known as Autotools).

   * re2c: http://re2c.org/
   * libjson-c: https://github.com/json-c/json-c
   * make

